<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="earthquake-n">earthquake <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɜːθkweɪk/    美 /'ɜːrθkweɪk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-quake">1.★ <strong>[C] 地震 (quake)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a slight / sharp / huge earthquake 
轻微/强烈/大地震</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On May 12, 2008, a severe earthquake destroyed almost everything in the school, leaving badly-damaged buildings.
2008年5月12日，一场强烈的地震几乎摧毁了学校里的一切，楼房受损严重。</p><footer>2011 福建书面表达</footer></div></div>